Btw here are the html code thing if you want to make one similar:


Open up "notepad" put this in it

[code]<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.1//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml11/DTD/xhtml11.dtd">
<html>
<head>
<title>Server Name</title>
<link href="style.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
</head>
<body>
<div id="wrapper">
<div id="banner">Server Name</div>
<div id="navigation"></div>
<div id="news"></div>
<div id="content"></div>
</div>
</body>
</html>[/code]

Save it as 
<blockquote>index.html</blockquote>


Now Open another Notepad put this in it.


[code]body {
	text-align: center;
